text Route_203_EventScript_Sign_1_Text
{
    "Rt. 203\n"
    "Jubilife City"
}

text Route_203_Text_Youngster_Michael_Intro
{
    "I get my get-up-and-go from my\n"
    "Pokémon!\p"
    "Here we go!\n"
    "Kricketot! Zubat!"
}

text Route_203_Text_Youngster_Michael_Defeated
{
    "Ack! My Pokémon..."
}

text Route_203_Text_Youngster_Michael_PostBattle
{
    "Keep out of the grass or dodge the\n"
    "eyes of Trainers...?\p"
    "rI always have a tough time choosing."
}

text Route_203_EventScript_Girl_Text
{
    "Your favorite Pokémon should be placed\n"
    "at the top left of your party list.\p"
    "That way, it will be the first to go out\n"
    "in a battle."
}

text Route_203_EventScript_Trainer_Tips_1_Text
{
    "Trainer Tips!\p"
    "rPokémon moves use energy called\n"
    "Power Points, or PP for short.\p"
    "If the PP of moves runs low, head for\n"
    "any Pokémon Center."
}

text Route_203_Text_Youngster_Dallas_Intro
{
    "I’m never apart from my Shinx.\n"
    "Our bond is strong!"
}

text Route_203_Text_Youngster_Dallas_Defeated
{
    "So sad...\n"
    "And so crushed..."
}

text Route_203_Text_Youngster_Dallas_PostBattle
{
    "I don’t bear grudges over losing.\n"
    "But I promise I’ll get tougher!"
}

text Route_203_Text_Youngster_Sebastian_Intro
{
    "Before I challenge the Pokémon Gym\n"
    "Leader, I’ll test my strength on you!"
}

text Route_203_Text_Youngster_Sebastian_Defeated
{
    "I guess it means I’m not ready for\n"
    "the Gym challenge yet..."
}

text Route_203_Text_Youngster_Sebastian_PostBattle
{
    "I guess if you don’t have a single\n"
    "Gym Badge, you’re a total nobody..."
}

text Route_203_Text_Lass_Kaitlin_Intro
{
    "I found a Trainer while looking for\n"
    "some Pokémon!"
}

text Route_203_Text_Lass_Kaitlin_Defeated
{
    "Hunh? You’re finished so soon?"
}

text Route_203_Text_Lass_Kaitlin_PostBattle
{
    "I walk through tall grass until I\n"
    "find the Pokémon I want."
}

text Route_203_EventScript_Trainer_Tips_2_Text
{
    "Trainer Tips!\p"
    "If a Pokémon is about to evolve,\n"
    "it can be instantly stopped.\p"
    "Press the B Button during evolution\n"
    "to startle the Pokémon into stopping.\p"
    "That is how evolution can be\n"
    "canceled."
}

text Route_203_Text_Lass_Madeline_Intro
{
    "I got a nifty-keen Gym Badge from\n"
    "the Gym Leader in Oreburgh City!"
}

text Route_203_Text_Lass_Madeline_Defeated
{
    "Oh, I lost! Lalala!"
}

text Route_203_Text_Lass_Madeline_PostBattle
{
    "I’m collecting lots of Gym Badges.\n"
    "They’re so sparkly and pretty!"
}

text Route_203_EventScript_Sign_2_Text
{
    "Rt. 203\n"
    "Oreburgh City"
}
